              <div>
                <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">MAZAK VARIAXIS i-500</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">日本马扎克5轴复合加工中心</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4">
