            <div class="text-center mb-4">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📐</div>
              <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Zeiss CONTURA G2</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">德国蔡司三坐标测量机</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
